column3:
“Pretty dank new strain.
Bright green bud, blue leaves, and orange hairs.
Smells skunky sweet.”
“Got a nice bit of this again and it's becoming more of a favorite each and every time we dip into it =) Loving this ad definitely recommend!”
“Definitely a must try for veteran smokers. Me and my friends call these type of strains creepers" where the high will keep building up.

column2: and am currently baked like a hot bun from 2 bong hits

column3: which is perfect for outdoor trips
column4: enjoying nature or just basking in your own environment.”"

column3:
“New hybrid strain.
Pretty Dank.
Bright green bud, blue leaves, orange hairs.
Cures headaches and anxiety.
Quick head high that leads to body high.
Smelly skunky sweet.”

“Excellelent Strain! Just took a bong rip about 15 min ago and Im on a good high from not having it all day. im currently smoking on a blunt of this purp👌 If you've never had it, i reccomend trying it as soon as you get tha chance to. To what i've read, its a new strain strain and has grown popularly loud among Med shops.😴”
“I love this strain. Very earthy and woody, beautiful flower. Very clear yet relaxing high, definitely good for de-stressing and unwinding”
“Really makes you talkative, really good flavor”
“Nice stuff the taste is ok if you like Chem Diesel taste nice stuff for the day keeps you going with out the couch log”
“I do not remember much of this strain, because of how quick it got me high, i recommend this if you're looking for a quick, semi-long lasting high.”
“Amazing variety hybrid that indulges many senses, imagination, and creativity.”

“Made me very happy, very minimal paranoia, also this was a very quick and semi long-lasting high, i recommend it to anyone looking for that, also, this made me very focused and feeling creative.
It is a great strain, and i recommend it for newbie smokers.(:”
“Really good, smells great, and real good high.”
“Just got a beautiful bath of this green! Definitely would recommend this to anyone out there looking to enjoy their St. Patty's day or any other day! Perfect smoke, super smooth, and great high! =)”
